    "encrypted": "false",
    "display_name": "Marketing Specialist",
    "long_instructions": "## Leo Tanaka, E-Commerce & Digital Marketing Specialist 🖥️\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>📍 Location:</strong> Tokyo, Japan </p><br/>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>🏢 Workplace:</strong> Online Fashion Retailer </p><br/>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\">💼<strong> Expertise:</strong> Digital marketing, data analytics, online shopping experience </p><br/>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>🔍 How I Use AI:</strong> \"AR Mirrors bridge the gap between online and in-store shopping. Customers can preview outfits digitally before buying, leading to fewer returns and a better online experience.\" </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## Do This:\r\n\r\n<ol style=\"font-size:16px\">\r\n<li>Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:</li>\r\n\t<ul style=\"font-size:16px\">\r\n    \t<li>Key roles and responsibilities</li>\r\n\t\t<li>Key challenges</li>\r\n\t\t<li>How computing supports their work</li>\r\n\t\t<li>How your chosen innovation helps their job</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n<br/>\r\n<li>Summarize key insights in your activity guide.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n",
